parameters: \nw[Shopkeeper]Welcome, please feel free to eat if you'd like.
\nw[Customer]I'm healed by that girl's smile~.
\nw[Female Mercenary]This is seriously hilarious~☆
\nw[Female Mercenary]That's right, hehe.
\nw[Ikesu]It's a town with a unique atmosphere, isn't it?
<ActiveMessage:口に合うといいんですけど>
\nw[Kuno]Heh, so you've traveled to various regions, huh?

\nw[Ikesu]Yeah, I've always admired adventurers. It's great
to see different places with my own eyes.

\nw[Taro](The man who saved me from the monsters... You've
come to this town, huh?)

\nw[Kuno]There's a shop where I work nearby. It's open at
night, so please come visit.

\nw[Ikesu]Kuno's shop... is it a... nighttime establishment?
I'm not really good with those kinds of places.
\nw[Kuno]It's okay, I'm not going to do anything.

\nw[Kuno]Well, it's a shop where people come expecting
something to happen, but we can just have a drink
and chat together if you prefer.

\nw[Kuno]Normally, there would be a fee for requesting a
specific staff member, but I'll cover the fee for
you, my benefactor, Ikesu-san.
\nw[Ikesu]It's not about the fee, but hmm...

\nw[Taro]If you'd like, please come. I also want to express
my gratitude.
\nw[Kuno]Oh, Taro.
\nw[Ikesu]Do you feel the same way?

\nw[Kuno]Yes, that's right. I'll prepare delicious sake and
snacks for you.

\nw[Ikesu]Alright, if you insist on saying that much, I'll
come visit next time.

\nw[Kuno]Thank goodness. I'll prepare everything properly
and wait for you.

\nw[Ikesu]I can't do it right away. I'll try working at this
guild for a while.
\nw[Kuno]Yes, I'll be looking forward to it.
<ActiveMessage:ここの雰囲気いいですよね>
\nw[Kuno]Please let me guide you around the town next time.
